snippet.title: Super Win the Game: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Throw on your nostalgia goggles and travel back in time with Super Win the Game, a retro-core explosion of exploration and platforming action!! 

Available October 1, 2014 for Windows, Mac, and Linux

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/310700/
itch.io: https://piratehearts.itch.io/super-win-the-game
Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/p/superwinthegame_storefront

See more at http://www.superwinthegame.com/
